 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>Ulaa</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> At 37 you will only just have enough mana to hold the spawn. If ST is resisting heavily, try a fear split. Fear one off and kill the other. As soon as the MOB is dead, sit and med like mad and wait for the other to come back.</P><P>Prob with these guys is the stupid DS's they cast on each other. The pet gets so badly hurt with the DS's, you then have to heal him at the end of each fight which takes quite a lot of mana.</P><P>Warlock<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=49001" target="_blank">Profile</a><BR><a href="http://www.domain-admins.com/Necro/index.shtml" target="_blank">Ulaa's web site</a><BR><img src="http://www.sizzlesites.com/Ulaa/steve.jpg"</img></font></td>
