        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Your cancel magic would take care of their DS.</P><P>If you want my opinion on a nice spot to hunt at 37 try the ulthorks in EW.</P><P>They're good xp and their rare drop is a tusk, you turn 4 of these in and get a rare gem or piece of jewelry.</P><P>So far I've gotten a blue diamond and a bracer that sold for 300pp to a merchant.</P><P>Just be careful of quad kiters and people, like Rhynn a lv51 druid on my server, taking spawns and saying they get xp, they greened out to a friend at lv 47 wizzie I was taling to at the time.</P><P>Malthusia Phyrexius<BR>Lv38 Geckomancer<BR>Morell Thule</P><P>"The last thing you hear as you draw your dying breath is the cackling of my skeletal pet"</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=318296" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=318296</a></font></td>
