 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>Kesik</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> When I did the EC spawns, I used the fear method.  I would target the ranger (if there was one) and fear him away (no darkness).<BR>Sic pet on the other and nuke with torbas 2 shots.<BR>Here's the part I haven't seen anyone else post, but work great for me.<BR>When the second one dies, sit and med - -have pet do the same (sit and heal).  When the first one comes back, FEAR him again.  Continue to med/heal.  Upon his 2nd return, send pet, nuke with lifetaps to regain hp.  Upon death, park pet at top of hill while you  sit and med and bottom of hill.  Pet will jump then the moment the spawn thus preventing them buffing.  They will go down extremely easy at this point.</P><P>Also, on a side note there is a vendor at the nearby in, single hut closest to druid hill named Firespinner.  She will Sell/Buy to a DE necro - how convenient (sp?)</P><P>Have fun !</P><P> </font></td>
